summary: This document appears to be a page from grand jury material listing charges against Jeffrey Epstein related to enticement of minors to engage in prostitution. It references multiple Jane Doe victims and specific counts and dates.

keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein faced charges of enticement of a minor to engage in prostitution in February 2005.
Epstein was also charged with conspiracy to entice a minor to engage in prostitution on December 18, 2004.
The document references multiple Jane Doe victims, specifically mentioning Jane Does #9-11, #10, and #11.
The document is marked as confidential grand jury material, indicating it contains sensitive information from grand jury proceedings.
